WEBVTT

00:01:29.000 --> 00:01:32.015
whether it's Apple or Martin Luther King
or the Wright brothers,

00:01:32.039 --> 00:01:35.976
they all think, act and communicate
the exact same way.

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:39.976
And it's the complete opposite
to everyone else.

00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:41.976
All I did was codify it,

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:45.976
and it's probably
the world's simplest idea.

00:01:46.000 --> 00:01:48.000
I call it the golden circle.

00:01:56.296 --> 00:01:58.976
Why? How? What?

00:01:59.000 --> 00:02:00.976
